<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THERE IS A PARADISE OF REST</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chawlhna ding Pielgal a um hi,
 Luipi gallam akhun;
 Zan thim lungkham um leh buoina khelah,
 Sepgim, kahna beita.

[V2]
 Ei tuokin! Aw ei tuokin!
 Zing nisuok khawvak hawih leh e'nna achun;
 Ei tuokin! Aw, ei tuokin!
 Zie luigal lam gam achun ei na tuokin!

[V3]
 2. Ziechun Khawpi vak hawih a um,
 Anawp zie gentheih loh;
 A lut tapoh in Lalpen chuh mu'n tin,
 A kawmah cheng un au.

[V4]
 3. Vanah Lallukhuk a um hi,
 Lal Krista'n a piek ding;
 Gunchuh taka A hungna ding ngakte,
 Leh Amah chawian cheng.

[V5]
 4. Tichun, thih chana ginum in,
 Van lam zuon zel hitiu;
 Hinna Kawtkhak I lut theihna dingun
 Gam nitum lohna ah.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>374</hymn_number>
</song>